
@startuml
|User|
start
:Requests to create a product;
|User|
|Client|
:Display form to create product;
:Input product data;
|Client|->:Sends create request with product details;
|Server|
:Saves product information;
|Database|
:Confirmation of successful creation;
|Database|
|Server|->|Client|:Sends creation success message;
stop

|User|
start
:Requests to update a product;
|User|
|Client|
:Display form to update product;
:Input new data;
|Client|->:Sends update request with modified product details;
|Server|
:Updates product information;
|Database|
:Confirmation of successful update;
|Database|
|Server|->|Client|:Sends update success message;
stop

|User|
start
:Requests to read a product;
|User|
|Client|->:Sends read request for product information;
|Server|
:Retrieves product information;
|Database|
:Sends product details;
|Database|
|Server|->|Client|:Sends product information;
stop
@enduml
